sub_title: Restaurant Manager at Restaurant Jamuna Indiaas
summary: Enthusiastic and hard-working Restaurant Manager with a winning attitude and desire to deliver an exceptional dining experience. Focused on setting high expectations and raising service standards. Savvy marketer with a track record of improving revenue, reducing turnover, and increasing customer satisfaction. I am very motivated, energetic and positive. I can work in a fast-paced, intercultural environment, as well as get along well with colleagues. My goal is to work in an organization that is passionate on making impact.
